{"type":"message","id":"557b797d","parentId":"f29ff12c","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:55:17.504Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经读取了 README.md。让我分析一下这个项目需要什么能力，然后对比我目前的能力，看看需要升级的地方。\n\n从 README.md 中可以看出这是一个多语言多媒体内容平台（MingoX），主要特点包括：\n\n1. **多语言双语内容** - 中英双语对照，需要词汇标注\n2. **内容形式** - 文字、图片、播客、视频\n3. **技术栈** - 纯静态 HTML/CSS/JS 站点，部署到 Gitee Pages 和 EdgeOne Pages\n4. **内容规范** - 有非常详细的词汇标注规范、标题格式、摘要规范等\n5. **抓取工具** - 使用 Playwright 抓取网页内容（反爬场景）\n\n让我查看一下当前项目的实际文件结构和内容，以更好地理解需要升级的地方。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我查看一下项目的实际文件结构和现有内容，以便更好地理解需要升级的地方："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:40","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /workspace/projects/workspace -type f \\( -name \"*.html\" -o -name \"*.css\" -o -name \"*.js\" \\) | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:41","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /workspace/projects/workspace/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":6262,"output":255,"cacheRead":46848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53365,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775037307746}}
