ot root 1489 Mar 29 12:16 MINGOX_TOKENS.md\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Mar 29 01:29 .openclaw\ndrwxr-xr-x  3 root root 4096 Mar 30 13:04 skills\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root 1673 Mar 29 01:29 SOUL.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root  860 Mar 29 01:29 TOOLS.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 root root  477 Mar 29 01:29 USER.md","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775037317536}}
{"type":"message","id":"d8419c7f","parentId":"7fe95231","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:55:21.722Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到项目结构了。MingoX 项目在 `/workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news/` 目录下。让我查看一下现有的文章示例，以便理解内容规范。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:42","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news/posts/2026-03-29-china-g7-europe-market.html"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:43","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news/index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":1079,"output":98,"cacheRead":52992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54169,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775037317541}}
{"type":"message","id":"429aa5db","parentId":"d8419c7f","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:55:21.740Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:42","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover\">\n    <title>拒赴G7与法国「对华关市」警告 | Skipping G7 & France's Market-Closure Warning | MingoX</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"中国拒绝出席G7峰会，法国警告欧洲市场可能对中国关闭。中欧贸易额超7800亿欧元，互为重要贸易伙伴。中英双语对照阅读。\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css/style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 导航栏 -->\n    <nav class=\"navbar\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"../\" class=\"logo\">🎙️ MingoX</a>\n            <div class=\"nav-links\">\n                <a href=\"../\">首页</a>\n                <a href=\"../about.html\">关于</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <!-- 主内容 -->\n    <main class=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <article class=\"post-content\">\n                    <h1>🌍 拒赴G7与法国「对华关市」警告<br><small class=\"title-en\">Skipping G7 & France's Market-Closure Warning</small></h1>\n\n                    <p>China <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">rebuffed</span><span class=\"word-info\">[rɪˈbʌft] v. 回绝（邀请）</span></span> the G7 Summit invitation; France issues <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">warning</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈwɔːnɪŋ] n. 警告</span></span>: European market may close to China.</p>\n\n                    <p>法国外长让-诺埃尔·巴罗在谈及中方对G7峰会的<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">rebuff</span><span class=\"word-info\">[rɪˈbʌf] n. 回绝</span></span>后公开表态：\"China faces risk of European market <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">closure</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈkləʊʒə] n. （市场）关闭</span></span>.\"</p>\n\n                    <p>原定于今年6月在加拿大举行的G7 summit，东道主国按<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">protocol</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈprəʊtəkɒl] n. 礼宾惯例</span></span>会邀请部分非成员国参会。今年加拿大邀请了中国，但中国已明确表态将<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">forgo</span><span class=\"word-info\">[fɔːˈɡəʊ] v. 不参加；放弃（出席）</span></span>G7峰会。</p>\n\n                    <p>过去几年，G7对中国的态度，从南海到台海，从贸易到技术 <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">sanctions</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈsæŋkʃənz] n. 制裁</span></span>，年年峰会年年谈中国，谈完之后发个 <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">communiqué</span><span class=\"word-info\">[kəˈmjuːnɪkeɪ] n. 公报</span></span>，措辞一年比一年强硬。中国拒绝出席，法国的<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">indignation</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˌɪndɪɡˈneɪʃn] n. 愤慨反应</span></span>甚于其他国家。</p>\n\n                    <p>巴罗说：\"如果中国不遵守 <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">multilateral</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˌmʌltɪˈlætərəl] adj. 多边的</span></span> 规则，那么欧洲市场对中国商品的开放，就不可能继续理所当然。\"</p>\n\n                    <p>2024年，中欧贸易 <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">turnover</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈtɜːnəʊvə] n. 成交额</span></span> 超过 7800 亿欧元。中国是欧盟第二大贸易伙伴，仅次于美国，欧盟是中国第一大贸易伙伴，双方经济<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">interdependence</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˌɪntədɪˈpendəns] n. 相互依存</span></span>极深。</p>\n\n                    <p>再看法国，2024年中法<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">bilateral</span><span class=\"word-info\">[baɪˈlætərəl] adj. 双边的</span></span>贸易额突破800亿欧元，中国是法国在亚洲最大的贸易伙伴。法国对华出口的主要商品，包括 <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">luxury</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈlʌkʃəri] n. 奢侈品</span></span>、农产品、航空设备、<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">cosmetics</span><span class=\"word-info\">[kɒzˈmetɪks] n. 化妆品</span></span>，每一个都是法国的支柱产业。</p>\n\n                    <p>欧盟贸易事务的决定权在欧洲委员会，不是法国能单方面<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">dictate</span><span class=\"word-info\">[dɪkˈteɪt] v. 强行左右</span></span>的。就算法国想在欧盟内部推动对华市场关闭，也须其他成员国<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">acquiescence</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˌækwiˈesns] n. 默许；认可</span></span>。</p>\n\n                    <p>但德国车企、荷兰 <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">lithography</span><span class=\"word-info\">[lɪˈθɒɡrəfi] n. 光刻</span></span> 设备、意大利制造业，哪一家愿意放弃中国市场？2023年，德国对华直接投资高达119亿欧元，创下<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">unprecedented</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ʌnˈpresɪdentɪd] adj. 空前的</span></span>纪录。</p>\n\n                    <p>法国之所以放这种狠话，明眼人都看得出来，这是欧洲国家惯用的negotiation <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">tactic</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈtæktɪk] n. 策略</span></span>。G7峰会还没开，中方已经拒绝出席，西方在<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">prestige</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈprestiːʒ] n. 声望；面子</span></span>上颇为受挫。</p>\n\n                    <p>作为欧洲主要大国，法国需要在舆论场上把<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">posturing</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈpɒstʃərɪŋ] n. 姿态性宣示</span></span>做足，至少让外界看起来，是中方不配合，不是我们没给机会。</p>\n\n                    <p>姿态归姿态，<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">substance</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈsʌbstəns] n. 实质</span></span>另当别论。法国外长发表言论后，法国外交部官网还发布了一份 <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">statement</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈsteɪtmənt] n. 声明</span></span>，强调与中国保持对话渠道畅通的重要性。</p>\n\n                    <p>同一时间，法国总统外事顾问正在与中方进行外交磋商，讨论的内容包括气候变化、全球<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">logistics</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ləˈdʒɪstɪks] n. 物流与供应链</span></span>稳定等，这些议题，哪一个离得开与中国合作？</p>\n\n                    <p>如果真要谈市场关闭，不妨先看<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">leverage</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈliːvərɪdʒ] n. 议价筹码</span></span>在谁手中。中国对欧出口的主力产品，是机电设备、光伏组件、电动汽车、消费电子，这些东西，欧洲短期内找不到 <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">alternative</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ɒːlˈtɜːnətɪv] n. 替代品</span></span>。</p>\n\n                    <p>2024年，欧盟从中国进口的电动汽车超过50万辆，占到欧盟电动车总进口量的四成以上，对华<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">dependency</span><span class=\"word-info\">[dɪˈpendənsi] n. 依赖度</span></span>已然不低。谈市场关闭，欧洲<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">backlash</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈbæklæʃ] n. 舆情反弹</span></span>难料？本土供给能否尽快<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">ramp</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ræmp] v. 放量拉升</span></span>？</p>\n\n                    <p>反过来，欧洲对华出口的主力，是高端制造、奢侈品、农产品，这些东西，中国同样可以<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">pivot</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈpɪvət] v. 转向</span></span>至其他市场。空客与奢侈品供给并非没有<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">substitutes</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈsʌbstɪtjuːts] n. 替代来源</span></span>，但失去中国这个全球最大的增量市场，欧洲企业将会付出沉重<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">toll</span><span class=\"word-info\">[təʊl] n. 代价</span></span>。</p>\n\n                    <p>时间<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">juncture</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈdʒʌŋktʃə] n. 关头</span></span>。欧洲经济目前处在高 <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">inflation</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ɪnˈfleɪʃn] n. 通胀</span></span>与<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">stagnation</span><span class=\"word-info\">[stæɡˈneɪʃn] n. 停滞</span></span>的泥潭里，德国连续两年经济零增长，法国公共债务占GDP比重超过110%，这时候谈关闭中国市场，不是在自讨苦吃吗？</p>\n\n                    <p>巴罗发言后的24小时内，法国 CAC40 指数中，对华出口占比高的几家公司股价小幅 <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">fluctuate</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈflʌktʃueɪt] v. 波动</span></span>，随后法国紧急表态后，才趋于稳定。</p>\n                </article>\n\n                <!-- 词汇表 -->\n                <div class=\"subtitle\">📖 重点词汇</div>\n                <div class=\"vocab-table-wrap\">\n                <table class=\"vocab-table\">\n                    <thead>\n                        <tr><th>词汇</th><th>音标</th><th>词性</th><th>释义</th></tr>\n                    </thead>\n                    <tbody>\n                        <tr><td>rebuffed</td><td>[rɪˈbʌft]</td><td>v.</td><td>回绝（邀请）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>warning</td><td>[ˈwɔːnɪŋ]</td><td>n.</td><td>警告</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>rebuff</td><td>[rɪˈbʌf]</td><td>n.</td><td>回绝</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>closure</td><td>[ˈkləʊʒə]</td><td>n.</td><td>（市场）关闭</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>protocol</td><td>[ˈprəʊtəkɒl]</td><td>n.</td><td>礼宾惯例</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>forgo</td><td>[fɔːˈɡəʊ]</td><td>v.</td><td>不参加；放弃（出席）</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>sanctions</td><td>[ˈsæŋkʃənz]</td><td>n.</td><td>制裁</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>communiqué</td><td>[kəˈmjuːnɪkeɪ]</td><td>n.</td><td>公报</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>indignation</td><td>[ˌɪndɪɡˈneɪʃn]</td><td>n.</td><td>愤慨反应</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>multilateral</td><td>[ˌmʌltɪˈlætərəl]</td><td>adj.</td><td>多边的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>turnover</td><td>[ˈtɜːnəʊvə]</td><td>n.</td><td>成交额</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>interdependence</td><td>[ˌɪntədɪˈpendəns]</td><td>n.</td><td>相互依存</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>bilateral</td><td>[baɪˈlætərəl]</td><td>adj.</td><td>双边的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>luxury</td><td>[ˈlʌkʃəri]</td><td>n.</td><td>奢侈品</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>cosmetics</td><td>[kɒzˈmetɪks]</td><td>n.</td><td>化妆品</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>dictate</td><td>[dɪkˈteɪt]</td><td>v.</td><td>强行左右</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>acquiescence</td><td>[ˌækwiˈesns]</td><td>n.</td><td>默许；认可</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>lithography</td><td>[lɪˈθɒɡrəfi]</td><td>n.</td><td>光刻</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>unprecedented</td><td>[ʌnˈpresɪdentɪd]</td><td>adj.</td><td>空前的</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>tactic</td><td>[ˈtæktɪk]</td><td>n.</td><td>策略</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>prestige</td><td>[ˈprestiːʒ]</td><td>n.</td><td>声望；面子</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>posturing</td><td>[ˈpɒstʃərɪŋ]</td><td>n.</td><td>姿态性宣示</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>substance</td><td>[ˈsʌbstəns]</td><td>n.</td><td>实质</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>statement</td><td>[ˈsteɪtmənt]</td><td>n.</td><td>声明</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>logistics</td><td>[ləˈdʒɪstɪks]</td><td>n.</td><td>物流与供应链</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>leverage</td><td>[ˈliːvərɪdʒ]</td><td>n.</td><td>议价筹码</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>alternative</td><td>[ɒːlˈtɜːnətɪv]</td><td>n.</td><td>替代品</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>dependency</td><td>[dɪˈpendənsi]</td><td>n.</td><td>依赖度</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>backlash</td><td>[ˈbæklæʃ]</td><td>n.</td><td>舆情反弹</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>ramp</td><td>[ræmp]</td><td>v.</td><td>放量拉升</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>pivot</td><td>[ˈpɪvət]</td><td>v.</td><td>转向</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>substitutes</td><td>[ˈsʌbstɪtjuːts]</td><td>n.</td><td>替代来源</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>toll</td><td>[təʊl]</td><td>n.</td><td>代价</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>juncture</td><td>[ˈdʒʌŋktʃə]</td><td>n.</td><td>关头</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>inflation</td><td>[ɪnˈfleɪʃn]</td><td>n.</td><td>通胀</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>stagnation</td><td>[stæɡˈneɪʃn]</td><td>n.</td><td>停滞</td></tr>\n                        <tr><td>fluctuate</td><td>[ˈflʌktʃueɪt]</td><td>v.</td><td>波动</td></tr>\n                    </tbody>\n                </table>\n                </div>\n                <!-- 返回链接 -->\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;\">\n                    <a href=\"../\" style=\"color: #667eea; text-decoration: none;\">← 返回首页</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <!-- 页脚 -->\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2026 MingoX | Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages | Powered by Gitee Pages</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script src=\"../js/main.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775037321733}}
{"type":"message","id":"43225d86","parentId":"429aa5db","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:55:21.745Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:43","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover\">\n    <title>MingoX - Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"MingoX - 多语言多媒体内容平台，用文字、图片、播客等形式分享新闻、思想与见解。Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"css/style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 导航栏 -->\n    <nav class=\"navbar\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"./\" class=\"logo\">🎙️ MingoX</a>\n            <div class=\"nav-links\">\n                <a href=\"./\">首页</a>\n                <a href=\"./about.html\">关于</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <!-- 主内容 -->\n    <main class=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <div class=\"site-intro\">\n                    <h1>🎙️ MingoX</h1>\n                    <p class=\"site-tagline\">Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages</p>\n                    <p class=\"site-desc\">用文字、图片、播客等多种形式，分享新闻、思想与见解</p>\n                </div>\n\n                <h2 class=\"page-title\">📰 最新发布</h2>\n\n                <ul class=\"post-list\">\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-elderly-ai-learning-needs.html\">👵 老年人AI学习需求研究<br><small class=\"title-en\">Study on Elderly AI Learning Needs: 6 Types & Standards</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-29 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ AI, 老年研究</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-elderly-ai-learning-needs.html\">基于237位老年人深度访谈的研究报告，揭示老年人AI学习的六大类型：老学霸、老顽童、老明星、老财迷、老当家、老伙伴。超半数学习者动机与能力提升、价值变现深度绑定...</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-ai-creation-golden-rules.html\">📝 AI创作黄金10条<br><small class=\"title-en\">AI Creation Golden Rules: 10 Ways to Stand Out</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-29 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ AI, 内容创作</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-ai-creation-golden-rules.html\">AI创作时代，如何让你的内容脱颖而出？这10条黄金法则，帮你打造杰出内容！从明确目标受众、善用但不依赖AI工具、打造个人IP到内容深度挖掘与情感共鸣，全面覆盖AI创作要点...</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-gold-price-analysis.html\">💰 金价跌破4500：联储按兵不动与4月回调风险<br><small class=\"title-en\">Gold Below $4,500: Fed on Hold & April Pullback Risk</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-29 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ 财经, 投资分析</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-gold-price-analysis.html\">金价从5400多美元跌至4491美元，跌幅近17%。美联储暂停降息、美元强势回归，市场预期2026年4月可能重演2015年暴跌剧本...</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-weekend-market-shock.html\">📈 油价飙升美股暴跌，国内融资松绑与消费补贴<br><small class=\"title-en\">Oil Spike, US Plunge: Refinance Easing & Subsidies</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-29 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ 财经, 市场分析</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-weekend-market-shock.html\">外围利空+国内利好双重夹击，A股下周如何应对？中东局势升级、油价暴涨、美股暴跌；国内政策组合拳，主板科技企业融资松绑，消费补贴落地...</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-27-kuaishou-ai-kling.html\">🎬 快手可灵ARR破3亿美元：AI投入如何被重估<br><small class=\"title-en\">Kling ARR Tops $300M: Re-rating Kuaishou AI</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-27 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ 科技, AI, 视频生成</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-27-kuaishou-ai-kling.html\">快手AI投入加大引发股价承压，可灵视频生成模型已现兑现迹象。年化收入超3亿美元，验证Token经济学商业模式...</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-china-g7-europe-market.html\">🌍 拒赴G7与法国「对华关市」警告<br><small class=\"title-en\">Skipping G7 & France's Market-Closure Warning</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-29 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ 国际关系, 贸易</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-29-china-g7-europe-market.html\">中方拒绝出席G7峰会，法国警告欧洲市场或对中国关闭。中欧贸易额超7800亿欧元，德国、荷兰、意大利等欧洲国家需要中国市场...</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-28-us-stock.html\">📈 美股抛售潮重创科技巨头<br><small class=\"title-en\">US Stock Sell-off Devastates Tech Giants</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2026-03-28 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ 财经, 科技</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2026-03-28-us-stock.html\">美股七巨头市值蒸发超8500亿美元，Meta因诉讼案暴跌11%，微软创2008年以来最差季度表现，通胀持续飙升引发成长股重创...</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"post-item\">\n                        <div class=\"post-title\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2025-05-21-google-io-gemini.html\">🤖 谷歌I/O：Gemini 2.5 Pro与AI搜索<br><small class=\"title-en\">Google I/O: Gemini 2.5 Pro & AI Search</small></a>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"post-meta\">📅 2025-05-21 | 📝 双语 | 🏷️ 科技, AI</div>\n                        <div class=\"post-excerpt\">\n                            <a href=\"posts/2025-05-21-google-io-gemini.html\">谷歌I/O 2025大会发布Gemini 2.5 Pro，月处理token达480万亿，推出智能体模式和AI模式搜索，重新定义搜索未来...</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <!-- 页脚 -->\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2026 MingoX | Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages | Powered by Gitee Pages</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script src=\"js/main.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775037321740}}
{"type":"message","id":"9e0c9981","parentId":"43225d86","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:55:48.115Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我对项目有了全面的了解。让我分析一下 README.md 中提到的要求与我当前能力的对比，然后提供需要升级的地方。\n\n从 README.md 看，MingoX 项目的核心需求：\n\n1. **内容创作能力**：\n   - 中英双语对照写作\n   - 词汇标注（`word-block` 格式）\n   - 标题、摘要、标签规范\n   - 外源素材改编（Playwright 抓取）\n\n2. **技术实现**：\n   - 纯静态 HTML/CSS/JS\n   - 部署到 Gitee Pages 和 EdgeOne Pages\n\n3. **质量控制**：\n   - 词汇密度检查（每句至少1处标注）\n   - 相邻 word-block 检查\n   - 词汇表一致性检查\n\n对比我当前的能力，我需要：\n\n1. **创建技能/工具来帮助生成符合规范的内容**\n2. **创建自动化检查工具来验证规范符合性**\n3. **更新 AGENTS.md 或创建 SKILL.md 来记录这些能力**\n\n让我创建一个全面的分析并实施升级。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"基于 README.md 的分析，我发现需要以下几个方面的升级来提升我协助 MingoX 项目的能力：\n\n## 📊 能力对比分析\n\n| 需求 | 当前状态 | 需要升级 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| **中英双语写作** | 基础能力具备 | 词汇标注格式自动化 |\n| **词汇密度检查** | 无 | 需要自动化检查脚本 |\n| **相邻 word-block 检查** | 需要手动运行命令 | 需要集成到工作流程 |\n| **外源素材抓取** | 有 Playwright 脚本 | 需要更好的集成和文档 |\n| **内容规范自检** | 人工检查 | 需要自动化工具 |\n\n让我开始实施这些升级："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:44","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# MingoX 内容助手\n\n协助 MingoX 项目创建符合规范的双语内容。\n\n## 能力范围\n\n### 1. 文章创建\n- 根据主题创建中英双语文章\n- 自动添加词汇标注（`word-block` 格式）\n- 生成符合规范的词汇表\n- 确保词汇密度（每句至少1处标注）\n\n### 2. 质量检查\n- 检查相邻 `word-block` 违规\n- 验证词汇表与正文一致性\n- 检查 HTML 结构合规性\n\n### 3. 发布流程\n- 更新 `index.html` 列表\n- 部署到 Gitee Pages\n- 部署到 EdgeOne Pages\n\n## 使用方式\n\n### 创建新文章\n```\n创建一篇关于 [主题] 的文章\n```\n\n### 检查文章合规性\n```\n检查 posts/YYYY-MM-DD-title.html 的规范性\n```\n\n### 部署网站\n```\nMX deploy\n```\n\n## 内容规范速查\n\n### 词汇标注格式\n```html\n<span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">word</span><span class=\"word-info\">[音标] 词性. 释义</span></span>\n```\n\n### 标题格式\n```html\n<h1>[emoji] 中文标题<br><small class=\"title-en\">English Title</small></h1>\n```\n\n### 标签规范\n- 内容形式：📝 文字、🖼️ 图片、🎙️ 播客、📹 视频\n- 语言类型：🌐 多语言、🇨🇳 中文、🇬🇧 英文\n- 主题标签：财经、科技、文化、观点\n\n## 不识别词汇清单（严格执行）\n\n### 第1类：非常简单的日常高频词\nyes, good, big, get, make, close, drop, go, see, take 等\n\n### 第2类：高中英语课程标准常见词\nprice, risk, trade, market, meeting, international, demand, flow, cancel, cost, gold, policy, chain, window, data, typical, emotion, giant, refuse, summit, domestic 等\n\n### 供应链表述\n优先用 **logistics** 等学科/行业上位词，**不要**单独标注 **chain**\n","file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/mingox-content-assistant/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":6534,"output":933,"cacheRead":54016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61483,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775037321745}}
