{"type":"message","id":"5bc5fe3f","parentId":"6c409529","timestamp":"2026-04-01T09:57:03.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要创建另一个实用的脚本，用于创建新文章的辅助工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:46","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# MingoX 文章模板生成器\n# 根据标题和日期生成符合规范的文章模板\n\nNEWS_DIR=\"/workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news\"\nPOSTS_DIR=\"$NEWS_DIR/posts\"\n\n# 显示帮助\nshow_help() {\n    cat << EOF\nMingoX 文章模板生成器\n\n用法:\n    $0 -t \"中文标题\" -e \"English Title\" -d YYYY-MM-DD -c \"分类\"\n\n选项:\n    -t  中文标题（必填）\n    -e  英文标题（必填）\n    -d  日期，格式 YYYY-MM-DD（默认：今天）\n    -c  分类标签，如：财经、科技、国际关系等（默认：综合）\n    -f  内容形式：text/image/podcast/video（默认：text）\n    -h  显示帮助\n\n示例:\n    $0 -t \"美联储利率决议前瞻\" -e \"Fed Rate Decision Preview\" -d 2026-04-02 -c \"财经\"\nEOF\n}\n\n# 默认值\nDATE=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nCATEGORY=\"综合\"\nFORM=\"text\"\nEMOJI=\"📝\"\n\n# 解析参数\nwhile getopts \"t:e:d:c:f:h\" opt; do\n    case $opt in\n        t) TITLE_CN=\"$OPTARG\" ;;\n        e) TITLE_EN=\"$OPTARG\" ;;\n        d) DATE=\"$OPTARG\" ;;\n        c) CATEGORY=\"$OPTARG\" ;;\n        f) FORM=\"$OPTARG\" ;;\n        h) show_help; exit 0 ;;\n        *) show_help; exit 1 ;;\n    esac\ndone\n\n# 验证必填参数\nif [ -z \"$TITLE_CN\" ] || [ -z \"$TITLE_EN\" ]; then\n    echo \"❌ 错误：中文标题和英文标题都是必填项\"\n    show_help\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# 根据内容形式设置 emoji\ncase $FORM in\n    text) EMOJI=\"📝\" ;;\n    image) EMOJI=\"🖼️\" ;;\n    podcast) EMOJI=\"🎙️\" ;;\n    video) EMOJI=\"📹\" ;;\nesac\n\n# 生成文件名\nFILENAME=$(echo \"$TITLE_CN\" | sed 's/[^a-zA-Z0-9\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]/-/g' | tr '[:upper:]' '[:lower:]')\nFILENAME=$(echo \"$FILENAME\" | sed 's/-\\+/-/g; s/^-//; s/-$//')\nFILEPATH=\"$POSTS_DIR/${DATE}-${FILENAME}.html\"\n\n# 检查文件是否已存在\nif [ -f \"$FILEPATH\" ]; then\n    echo \"⚠️  警告：文件已存在: $FILEPATH\"\n    read -p \"是否覆盖? (y/N): \" confirm\n    if [ \"$confirm\" != \"y\" ] && [ \"$confirm\" != \"Y\" ]; then\n        echo \"已取消\"\n        exit 0\n    fi\nfi\n\n# 生成 HTML 模板\ncat > \"$FILEPATH\" << EOF\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover\">\n    <title>${TITLE_CN} | ${TITLE_EN} | MingoX</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"${TITLE_CN} - ${TITLE_EN}。中英双语对照阅读。\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css/style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <!-- 导航栏 -->\n    <nav class=\"navbar\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"../\" class=\"logo\">🎙️ MingoX</a>\n            <div class=\"nav-links\">\n                <a href=\"../\">首页</a>\n                <a href=\"../about.html\">关于</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <!-- 主内容 -->\n    <main class=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <article class=\"post-content\">\n                    <h1>${EMOJI} ${TITLE_CN}<br><small class=\"title-en\">${TITLE_EN}</small></h1>\n\n                    <p>英文导语（一句话概括全文核心）：...</p>\n\n                    <p>第一段正文，每句需包含至少一个 <span class=\"word-block\"><span class=\"english-word\">sample</span><span class=\"word-info\">[ˈsɑːmpl] n. 示例</span></span> 词汇标注。</p>\n\n                    <p>继续正文...</p>\n\n                    <!-- 更多段落... -->\n                </article>\n\n                <!-- 外源稿来源说明（如果是外源综述稿） -->\n                <!--\n                <div class=\"post-source-footer\" style=\"margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #667eea; border-radius: 4px;\">\n                    <p><strong>📌 来源说明</strong></p>\n                    <p>本文基于 [来源平台/账号] 的公开内容整理改编，原文链接：<a href=\"[原文URL]\" target=\"_blank\">[原文URL]</a></p>\n                    <p>本站条目为学习整理用途，不构成投资建议。转载请联系原权利人。</p>\n                </div>\n                -->\n\n                <!-- 词汇表 -->\n                <div class=\"subtitle\">📖 重点词汇</div>\n                <div class=\"vocab-table-wrap\">\n                <table class=\"vocab-table\">\n                    <thead>\n                        <tr><th>词汇</th><th>音标</th><th>词性</th><th>释义</th></tr>\n                    </thead>\n                    <tbody>\n                        <tr><td>sample</td><td>[ˈsɑːmpl]</td><td>n.</td><td>示例</td></tr>\n                        <!-- 添加更多词汇 -->\n                    </tbody>\n                </table>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- 返回链接 -->\n                <div style=\"margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;\">\n                    <a href=\"../\" style=\"color: #667eea; text-decoration: none;\">← 返回首页</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <!-- 页脚 -->\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2026 MingoX | Multimedia Post in Mixed Languages | Powered by Gitee Pages</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script src=\"../js/main.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ 文章模板已生成: $FILEPATH\"\necho \"\"\necho \"📋 下一步：\"\necho \"1. 编辑文件填写正文内容\"\necho \"2. 添加词汇标注（每句至少1处）\"\necho \"3. 完善词汇表\"\necho \"4. 运行 ./scripts/check-content.sh 检查合规性\"\necho \"5. 更新 index.html 添加文章链接\"\necho \"\"\necho \"📖 写作规范参考:\"\necho \"- 词汇标注格式: <span class=\\\"word-block\\\"><span class=\\\"english-word\\\">word</span><span class=\\\"word-info\\\">[音标] 词性. 释义</span></span>\"\necho \"- 避免相邻 word-block（两个标注之间必须有中文/标点间隔）\"\necho \"- 词汇表必须与正文标注一一对应\"\n","file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/MingoX/news/scripts/create-post.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":1556,"output":1876,"cacheRead":61440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64872,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775037380557}}
